HEADWORD: Chilling
<hw>Chill"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Making chilly or
cold; depressing; discouraging; cold; distant; <as>as, a
<ex>chilling</ex> breeze; a <ex>chilling</ex> manner</as>.</def></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Chill"ing"ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

